      "cooked": "<p>Hey Guys!<br>\nI use Trainerday with my Elite Direto Trainer and I am happy with it so far!<br>\nThe only Problem I get is when i do Intervall training with Trainerday\u2026  If I do for example 1 min Off / 1 Min on and my cadence drops during the ON part it gets almost impossible to get back into the \u201cnormal\u201d cadence.<br>\nI get a similar problem in the beginning of workouts: If I start pedaling After having started the workout, the resistance is much higher than actually set. If i start the workout while already pedaling, the problem does not occur.<br>\nHow can i adjust the app, to not get theses symptoms? Thanks and BR</p>",
